45
00:09:00.791 --> 00:09:02.791
<i>I think he's trying to tell me something.</i>

46
00:09:03.791 --> 00:09:06.500
<i>Or maybe I just want him</i>
<i>to tell me something.</i>

47
00:09:06.583 --> 00:09:08.291
